title: 592. Breaking Down Patrick Mahomes & Lamar Jackson's Play in MNF Game
itunes:title: 592. Breaking Down Patrick Mahomes & Lamar Jackson's Play in MNF Game
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys discuss Bills QB Josh Allen's play and season so far (1:15). After that, the pair break down the game of Chiefs QB Patrick Mahomes and Ravens QB Lamar Jackson after the Chiefs' MNF win (10:16). Next, the duo react to Cardinals WR Larry Fitzgerald's interview on playing in a COVID-19 environment, which was with Steve Wyche and Jim Trotter from the "Huddle and Flow" podcast (27:38). To wrap up the show, the guys discuss how Air Raid quarterbacks are having success and also look back at last year's Alabama and LSU wide receivers (32:59).
